" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 21, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104mxt1665702792020.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mxt1665702792020.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mxt1665702792020.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"mxt1665702792020\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Define Field Interface\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specify the value of the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Database Interface</span> property of a field, which specifies how the field is stored. \n \n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mxt1665702792020__p_d5243e1_d5244e1_d5245e1\">If you have created modeled field interface, click <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Use modeled</span> to select the one you want to use. This is useful when you want to use the same interface for multiple fields.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mxt1665702792020__p_d5246e1_d5247e1_d5248e1\">It is possible to define sub-field definitions, variable-length techniques, and use of I/O translation tables by clicking <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">More</span>. Normally, you do not need to consider these definitions. They are intended only for existing databases that support these features.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mxt1665702792020__section_hd2_nzs_lcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d576021e70\">Fields </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"mxt1665702792020__ul_jxb_4zs_lcc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mxt1665702792020__li_d2270e1_d2271e1_d2272e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nkv1665702792163.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nkv1665702792163.html\" title=\"Data type of the selected parameter. The default value is String.\">Data Type</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mxt1665702792020__li_d2273e1_d2274e1_d2275e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vzh1665702711081.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vzh1665702711081.html\" title=\"Data packing code for the field.\">Data Packing</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mxt1665702792020__li_d2276e1_d2277e1_d2278e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vcl1665702711151.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vcl1665702711151.html\" title=\"Physical length of the field in the database, in characters.\">Fixed Length of Field</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530128\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530128\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Define Field Interface Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Define Field Interface Specify the value of the Database Interface property of a field, which specifies how the field is stored. If you have created modeled field interface, click Use modeled to select the one you want to use. This is useful when you want to use the same interface for multiple fields. It is possible to define sub-field definitions, variable-length techniques, and use of I/O translation tables by clicking More . Normally, you do not need to consider these definitions. They are intended only for existing databases that support these features. Fields Data Type Data Packing Fixed Length of Field Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}